<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q26_v3" title="Q26_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Un club deportivo compró 30 botellas de agua por $21 000 y 10 cajas de jugo por $25 000.</p>
    <p>Se indica que el costo total es proporcional a la cantidad de unidades de cada producto. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el costo total, en pesos, al comprar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas de agua y <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> cajas de jugo?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El precio de una botella de agua es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y el de una caja de jugo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces, al comprar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> unidades de cada producto, el costo total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>46&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>30</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn>
              <m:mn>10</m:mn>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>⋅</m:mo>
            <m:mi>x</m:mi>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El costo por botella de agua es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y el costo por caja de jugo es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, comprar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas y <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> cajas cuesta <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>+</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión no representa un costo proporcional a <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, porque queda <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>630&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>250&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>. Un contraejemplo concreto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>: la opción C da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>630&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>250&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>63&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>88&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero el costo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7000</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>88&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, la opción no sirve.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mfrac>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn>
                <m:mo>+</m:mo>
                <m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mi>x</m:mi>
            </m:mfrac>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta expresión es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>46&#160;000</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, y no representa un costo proporcional a <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>. Un contraejemplo concreto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>: la opción D da <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>46&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4600</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, pero el costo correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mn>10</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4600</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>32&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, la expresión no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular el precio unitario de cada producto</strong></p>
            <p>Como 30 botellas de agua cuestan $21 000, una botella cuesta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Como 10 cajas de jugo cuestan $25 000, una caja cuesta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Expresar el costo de comprar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> unidades de cada producto</strong></p>
            <p>El costo de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> botellas de agua es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>El costo de <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math> cajas de jugo es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Sumar ambos costos</strong></p>
            <p>El costo total es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3200</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La alternativa B escribe exactamente ese mismo razonamiento con precios unitarios:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>⋅</m:mo><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>21&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>700</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>25&#160;000</m:mn><m:mn>10</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esa expresión equivale a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>3200</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión correcta es la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>